text: Corvette K-225 is a 1943 American World War II drama movie directed by Richard Rosson and produced by Howard Hawks. It stars Randolph Scott, James Brown, Ella Raines, Robert Mitchum, Noah Beery, Jr., Andy Devine, Murray Alper and was distributed by Universal Pictures. It was nominated for an Academy Award in 1944. ==Other websites== * * * * * Category:1943 war movies Category:1943 drama movies Category:American war movies Category:American drama movies Category:World War II movies Category:Movies directed by Richard Rosson Category:Universal Pictures movies Category:Movies set in Nova Scotia Category:Movies about the Royal Navy Category:Movies set on ships
